### 2. REGISTER - Nuovo utente
POST http://localhost:23109/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "mofawab461@herojp.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!",
  "username": "alice1234",
  "nome": "Alice",
  "cognome": "Rossi"
}
### 3. Login - Ottieni token per autenticazione
POST http://localhost:23109/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "mofawab461@herojp.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.token);
    client.global.set("user_id", response.body.user.id);
    console.log("✓ Token salvato: " + response.body.token.substring(0, 20) + "...");
    console.log("✓ User ID: " + response.body.user.id);
%}


### 1. GET PROFILE - Ottieni profilo dell'utente autenticato (Alice)
GET http://localhost:23109/api/v1/account
Authorization: Bearer {{ auth_token }}

### 2. GET PROFILE - Senza token (dovrebbe fallire 401)
GET http://localhost:23109/api/v1/account

### 3. MODIFICA USERNAME - Valido
PATCH http://localhost:23109/api/v1/account/username
Authorization: Bearer {{ auth_token }}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice_nuovo"
}

### 4. MODIFICA USERNAME - Troppo corto (dovrebbe fallire 400)
PATCH http://localhost:23109/api/v1/account/username
Authorization: Bearer {{ auth_token }}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "al"
}

### 5. MODIFICA EMAIL - Valida (richiede invio email e verifica)
PATCH http://localhost:23109/api/v1/account/email
Authorization: Bearer {{ auth_token }}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "mofawab461@herojp.com"
}

### 6. MODIFICA EMAIL - Non valida (dovrebbe fallire 400)
PATCH http://localhost:23109/api/v1/account/email
Authorization: Bearer {{ auth_token }}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "email-non-valida"
}

### 7. ELIMINA ACCOUNT - Anonimizza ed elimina account dell'utente autenticato
DELETE http://localhost:23109/api/v1/account
Authorization: Bearer {{ auth_token }}
